[
  {
    "startTime": 0.2,
    "endTime": 6.3,
    "text": "The following is a rebroadcast of Tuesday's presidential debate, even though Tuesday feels like a hundred days ago."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.5,
    "endTime": 11.0,
    "text": "We thought it was important to see it again, since it might be the only presidential debate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.0,
    "endTime": 15.0,
    "text": "And it was pretty fun to watch, as long as you don't live in America."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.6,
    "endTime": 27.0,
    "text": "Good evening. I'm your moderator, Chris Wallace."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.0,
    "endTime": 35.0,
    "text": "And I think I'm gonna do a really, really good job tonight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.7,
    "endTime": 40.0,
    "text": "First, I want to lay out the rules, which both parties agreed to in advance."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.0,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "Each candidate will have two minutes, uninterrupted."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.4,
    "endTime": 46.0,
    "text": "Boring."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.1,
    "endTime": 49.0,
    "text": "Mr. President, I haven't even introduced the candidates yet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.0,
    "endTime": 51.5,
    "text": "Tell that to my Adderall, Chris."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.6,
    "endTime": 55.0,
    "text": "Now let's get this show on the road and off the rails."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.8,
    "endTime": 58.599999999999994,
    "text": "And you did take the COVID test you promised to take in advance, correct?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.8,
    "endTime": 62.3,
    "text": "Absolutely. Scout's honor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.5,
    "endTime": 68.0,
    "text": "Well, President Trump has already introduced himself, so let's now welcome the Democratic candidate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.0,
    "endTime": 69.4,
    "text": "Boo. Here comes the booing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.8,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "Former vice president of the United States."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.3,
    "endTime": 73.0,
    "text": "Allegedly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.1,
    "endTime": 75.39999999999999,
    "text": "And senator from Delaware."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.5,
    "endTime": 76.7,
    "text": "Not even a real state."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.7,
    "endTime": 79.0,
    "text": "Joe Biden."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.0,
    "endTime": 96.0,
    "text": "Mr. Vice president."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.8,
    "endTime": 98.0,
    "text": "Just one second, Chris."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.6,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.4,
    "endTime": 111.0,
    "text": "It looks like..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.0,
    "endTime": 114.0,
    "text": "It looks like you're ready to debate, Joe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.0,
    "endTime": 116.0,
    "text": "Absolutely not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.0,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "I've got the beginning of 46 thoughts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "Now let's do this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.0,
    "endTime": 125.0,
    "text": "I'm holding my bladder. Let's get at her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.0,
    "endTime": 131.0,
    "text": "Tonight we'll be discussing six major topics, none of which anyone will remember by tomorrow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.0,
    "endTime": 133.0,
    "text": "We begin with the Supreme Court."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.5,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "President Trump, two minutes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.0,
    "endTime": 138.0,
    "text": "I'm gonna do ten."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.0,
    "endTime": 140.0,
    "text": "I'd like to begin with a list of complaints."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.4,
    "endTime": 143.5,
    "text": "People are mean to me. Joe here is very mean."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.6,
    "endTime": 145.0,
    "text": "Chris Wallace is mean."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 147.0,
    "text": "The economy is mean."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.0,
    "endTime": 150.0,
    "text": "It keeps losing jobs, which is mean to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.0,
    "endTime": 159.2,
    "text": "And the China virus has been very mean to me by being a hoax, and that statement will not come back to haunt me later this week."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.4,
    "endTime": 163.4,
    "text": "And-and what about the question I asked you about the Supreme Court?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.6,
    "endTime": 165.0,
    "text": "I think I answered that already."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.4,
    "endTime": 171.8,
    "text": "We're very excited about our nominee, Amy Cristina Barcelona, and it was so nice..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.0,
    "endTime": 177.5,
    "text": "so nice to welcome her the other day with open arms and uncovered faces."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.7,
    "endTime": 180.5,
    "text": "Mr. Vice President, same question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.6,
    "endTime": 181.5,
