  {
    "startTime": 185.5,
    "endTime": 187.0,
    "text": "No, it's not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.0,
    "endTime": 189.0,
    "text": "Excuse me. Please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.0,
    "endTime": 191.7,
    "text": "No, whatever you're gonna say, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.8,
    "endTime": 193.8,
    "text": "Mr. President, please let him speak."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.0,
    "endTime": 196.0,
    "text": "He let you speak. Now let him speak."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.2,
    "endTime": 196.89999999999998,
    "text": "But he's lying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.1,
    "endTime": 200.1,
    "text": "I can't point out if he says a lie?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.3,
    "endTime": 202.0,
    "text": "I said two words, you son of a..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.0,
    "endTime": 204.0,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.0,
    "endTime": 207.8,
    "text": "Don't do it, Joe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.0,
    "endTime": 209.0,
    "text": "That's exactly what he wants."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.0,
    "endTime": 214.0,
    "text": "Don't let your inner Whitey Bulger come out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.0,
    "endTime": 221.8,
    "text": "Just flash them all that smile they taught you in anger management."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.0,
    "endTime": 231.0,
    "text": "Now, Mr. Vice President, and only Mr. Vice President, would you consider adding additional justices to the Supreme Court?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.0,
    "endTime": 232.0,
    "text": "He won't even answer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.0,
    "endTime": 234.0,
    "text": "I just asked the question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.4,
    "endTime": 245.3,
    "text": "And he won't even answer it, just like he won't answer what about his son Hunter and Burisma and the mayor of Moscow and Obama was spying on me and he emailed Benghazi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.5,
    "endTime": 249.0,
    "text": "Mr. President, no one understands what you're saying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.0,
    "endTime": 257.0,
    "text": "You're just listing terms you heard on Fox News and it sounds like you're saying the names of characters from a season four of a show that no one has watched."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.1,
    "endTime": 259.56,
    "text": "Sheriff of Portland."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.56,
    "endTime": 263.6,
    "text": "Mr. Vice President, please answer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.6,
    "endTime": 267.0,
    "text": "Now look, here's the deal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.0,
    "endTime": 269.6,
    "text": "Can I respond to that, Chris?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.6,
    "endTime": 274.70000000000005,
    "text": "Will you just shut up?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.7,
    "endTime": 276.0,
    "text": "Sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.0,
    "endTime": 278.8,
    "text": "I'm sorry, I misspoke."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.0,
    "endTime": 302.6,
    "text": "What I meant to say was I'd appreciate it very much if you could just allow me to finish my responses as opposed to sabotaging every waking moment with a toxic geyser of verbal diarrhea you cracked out turd-hurling sack of rancid dog snot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.8,
    "endTime": 306.5,
    "text": "Losing control."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.5,
    "endTime": 308.4,
    "text": "Back to you, Chris."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.6,
    "endTime": 311.0,
    "text": "You still have two minutes, Joe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 311.0,
    "endTime": 315.0,
    "text": "Oh, really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.5,
    "endTime": 320.0,
