    "text": "You just wear it when you're backing out of the driveway, then you take it off, okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 369.9,
    "endTime": 377.2,
    "text": "But Joe wears the biggest mask I've ever seen, and he's standing, like, 200 feet away from everybody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.4,
    "endTime": 386.4,
    "text": "Look, man, I'm a nice guy, but if you give me any more guff tonight, I'll rip your face off like a mad chimp."
