  {
    "startTime": 639.0,
    "endTime": 640.5,
    "text": "I didn't even know any of these groups."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 640.6,
    "endTime": 646.1,
    "text": "I certainly wouldn't even know how to signal them if I tried."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.1,
    "endTime": 648.9,
    "text": "America, are you listening to this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 649.0,
    "endTime": 656.2,
    "text": "The president of the United States is literally blowing a dog whistle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 656.3,
    "endTime": 657.54,
    "text": "I don't think this thing is working."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 657.54,
    "endTime": 658.6999999999999,
    "text": "I don't hear anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 658.7,
    "endTime": 661.0,
    "text": "Mr. Vice President, your closing statement."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 662.0,
    "endTime": 663.0,
    "text": "Well..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664.0,
    "endTime": 665.0,
    "text": "That is so unfair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 665.0,
    "endTime": 666.7,
    "text": "Why don't I get to make a closing statement first?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 666.9,
    "endTime": 669.0,
    "text": "After all, I am the pres..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 682.6,
    "endTime": 686.3000000000001,
    "text": "Sorry, but I think we all needed a break."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 686.5,
    "endTime": 689.8,
    "text": "Isn't that satisfying?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 690.0,
    "endTime": 699.3,
    "text": "Just not to hear his voice for a single goddamn second."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 699.4,
    "endTime": 700.9,
    "text": "Let's wallow in it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 701.0,
    "endTime": 704.8,
    "text": "Let's bask in the Trump-less-ness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 705.0,
    "endTime": 710.0,
    "text": "Now, Chris, could I speak directly to the American people?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 711.9,
    "endTime": 713.0,
    "text": "Is it gonna be weird?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 713.2,
    "endTime": 715.0,
    "text": "Totally."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 715.0,
    "endTime": 717.0,
    "text": "Totally weird."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 717.0,
    "endTime": 721.7,
    "text": "America, look at me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 721.7,
    "endTime": 725.7,
    "text": "Look directly into my eyeballs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 725.7,
    "endTime": 734.4000000000001,
    "text": "You can trust me because I believe in science and karma."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 734.5,
    "endTime": 750.0,
    "text": "Now, just imagine if science and karma could somehow team up to send us all a message about how dangerous this virus can be."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 758.0,
    "endTime": 762.5,
    "text": "I'm not saying I want it to happen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 762.5,
    "endTime": 778.2,
    "text": "Just imagine if it did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 778.3,
    "endTime": 786.8,
    "text": "So, this November, please get on the Biden train, which is literally a commuter train to Delaware."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 787.0,
    "endTime": 792.9,
    "text": "And we can all make America not actively on fire again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 792.9,
    "endTime": 794.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 795.3,
    "endTime": 797.0,
    "text": "Now I'll unpause him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 797.5,
    "endTime": 799.0,
    "text": "Antifa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 799.0,
    "endTime": 801.1,
    "text": "Nope, can't do it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 801.1,
    "endTime": 803.3000000000001,
    "text": "Gonna leave him on pause."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 803.3,
    "endTime": 805.0,
    "text": "Oh, and one more thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 805.0,
    "endTime": 809.0,
    "text": "Live from New York, Saturday Night Live!"
  }
]